        <h2>Character Profile: Tanjiro Kamado</h2>
        <p><img src="/images/demon.jpg" alt="Tanjiro Kamado" style="width:100px;height:auto;"></p>
        <p><strong>Name:</strong> Tanjiro Kamado</p>
        <p><strong>Role:</strong> Protagonist, Demon Slayer</p>
        <p><strong>Breathing Technique:</strong> Water Breathing, Sun Breathing</p>
        <p>Tanjiro Kamado is a compassionate and determined Demon Slayer whose goal is to find a cure for his sister Nezuko, who has been turned into a demon. Tanjiro is known for his keen sense of smell, which aids him in tracking demons.</p>
